# Tree of Wisdom (AI + IoT Plant System)

## Overview
Tree of Wisdom is an AI-powered plant monitoring system that generates poetic responses based on environmental data using ChatGPT API. :contentReference[oaicite:3]{index=3}

---

## Features
- Soil moisture sensing
- Temperature & humidity monitoring
- Light intensity detection
- AI-generated poetic responses
- OLED display output

---

## Concepts
- Artificial Intelligence
- IoT Systems
- Sensor Data Processing
- Natural Language Generation

---

## Components
- ESP8266 / ESP32
- DHT11 Sensor
- Soil Moisture Sensor
- LDR
- OLED Display
- Speaker (optional)

---

## Working
- Sensors collect environmental data
- Data sent to AI model
- AI generates poetic output
- Output displayed on screen

---

## Applications
- Smart agriculture
- Educational AI projects
- Interactive IoT systems

